				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%AFc-chinh-B%E1%BA%AFc-quy-ch%C3%AD-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-m%E1%BA%B7c-ch%E1%BA%BF-ph%C3%B3ng-v%C3%A3ng-Phu-Ch%C3%A2u-t%C3%A1c/poem-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Bắc chinh - Bắc quy chí Phụng Tường, mặc chế phóng vãng Phu Châu tác - 北征－北歸至鳳翔，墨制放往鄜州作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-B%C3%A1-K%E1%BB%B3/C%C3%A1o-n%E1%BA%A1n-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-f3Sh-6-GUW4jOaFOFi1z0w">Cáo nạn biểu - 告難表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-B%C3%A1-K%E1%BB%B3/author-hC5Mmn2w17BNNvwatnvA8Q">Bùi Bá Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/C%E1%BB%ADu-ni%C3%AAn-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BA%A5t-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BA%A5t-nh%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%A3m-s%E1%BB%B1-nhi-t%C3%A1c-K%E1%BB%B3-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-du-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-L479NoEHrQVwO7qKgqDOZA">Cửu niên thập nhất nguyệt nhị thập nhất nhật cảm sự nhi tác (Kỳ nhật độc du Hương Sơn tự) - 九年十一月二十一日感事而作（其日獨遊香山寺）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-M%E1%BB%99ng-Qu%E1%BA%BF/Giao-long-ca/poem-UzZVXlxNbHMu35-YK2oCMQ">Giao long ca - 蛟龍歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-M%E1%BB%99ng-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-WQSsQH4AKF_2NXEwk59aDA">Hà Mộng Quế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ngu-C%C6%A1/poem-XhOmTPUKEBOySNOT7ZvZiQ">Ngu Cơ - 虞姬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%E1%BB%87p-giang/poem-csh8ujkV1cSEGuoKbE1Ufg">Thiệp giang - 涉江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0nh/V%C4%83n-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%E1%BA%A5n-V%C5%A9-chi-ng%E1%BB%A5c/poem-gpJ0z9eelL0PEF4D4-ViEg">Văn Trương Chấn Vũ chi ngục - 聞張振武之獄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0nh/author-8k5-bGU03Z_txBNZHdLGbQ">Liên Hoành</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
